Package com.github.tadukoo.view.border

Class NoBorder

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.border.AbstractBorder
com.github.tadukoo.view.border.NoBorder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Border
public class NoBorder extends AbstractBorder
No Border is an implementation of AbstractBorder that works as no Border. This is for use when you need to specify a Border, but don't actually want one (i.e. null doesn't mean no border for some reason).

Alpha v.0.3
